{"tid":1697255,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］想幫科大手足就入黎！","createTime":"2019-11-06T17:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T18:12:04.000Z","uid":71262,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9ff8c3e32111676c156a7f5fd4d6b976f36f1f2f","tid":1697255,"uid":71262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T17:17:59.000Z","msg":"大家都當梓樂係自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發現佢屋企人未必會睇連儂牆上面講啲咩<br />\n<br />\n所以建議大家寫慰問卡 心意卡<br />\n<br />\n等佢地可以帶返屋企慢慢睇 而且內容唔公開<br />\n<br />\n最重要最重要最重要係可以將大家最真心既說話講比梓樂同佢屋企人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等佢屋企人同樂樂知道手足係有幾關心佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n熟悉樂樂既朋友同同學又有佢家人電話我建議直接打比佢父母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登得文字 冇一個人可以實實在在比佢地知道我地既真實想法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係又唔想太麻煩到佢家人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好矛盾..<br />\n<br />\n但有個建議比大家<br />\n<br />\n將心比己 如果我作為受害者家人 我覺得未必有興趣聽到點樣報仇 抗爭 <br />\n<br />\n對佢地黎講可能係二次傷害 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以希望大家將焦點放係我地點樣關心梓樂同佢家人<br />\n<br />\n動之以情 我都好希望可以說服到佢屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等佢地感受到手足對梓樂既關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n寫完心意卡可以交去醫院病房門口連儂牆果個位 佢地會拎返去架<br />\n<br />\n當然手足想點我係知啦 但關鍵都係佢地屋企人<br />\n<br />\n重要野講三次<br />\n寫慰問卡 心意卡 然後交去醫院病房門口連儂牆果個位<br />\n寫慰問卡 心意卡 然後交去醫院病房門口連儂牆果個位<br />\n寫慰問卡 心意卡 然後交去醫院病房門口連儂牆果個位<br />\n<br />\n仲有呀 手足可唔可以錄一啲想同梓樂講既說話 唱歌都得架 最好有人一次過整落mp3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想過咗探病時間都播到比佢聽 就好似我地一齊陪住佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴絲諗到咩建議connect佢屋企人請提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 幫到手足自爆都冇所謂喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd96818fb1eec3d558127ac4a5b3a83957d4ceaa","tid":1697255,"uid":71262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T17:40:06.000Z","msg":"點解完全冇人既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a47d347ca8671fd6de71f1c2b4762bd37b2e6261","tid":1697255,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T17:41:04.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"af4a461a01ff1a6e32c7607f1f9c6a4f86d40df1","tid":1697255,"uid":261735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T17:42:56.000Z","msg":"pushhhhhh"},{"pid":"3bb889117fd3c9f9f305bf47be98209270825efe","tid":1697255,"uid":71262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T17:56:20.000Z","msg":"寫心意卡呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa1aaa9c6209c101a4bfd8760cacc7d9a20c371","tid":1697255,"uid":71262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T17:58:04.000Z","msg":"最緊要梓樂朋友同佢同學睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b826ef60590f526d8e67e866f0137c4b9af62250","tid":1697255,"uid":227921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T17:58:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6da8a68c5fa60be2cccd773a5b16126540cf8997","tid":1697255,"uid":131481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T17:59:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"62a541f607490fb3c4c57af57544f1d4e9868ec6","tid":1697255,"uid":31205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T18:00:22.000Z","msg":"希望有奇蹟發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n煲底見好無呀梓樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c675bc3